criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All individuals aged over 18 years who signed the informed consent and had lesions in
             native coronary arteries treated only with Inspiron Sirolimus-Eluting stent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Saphenous vein grafts or Mammary lesions;

          -  Individuals who have been treated within the last 6 months with another stent;

          -  Acute myocardial infarction with ST segment elevation;

          -  Chronic Total Occlusion
